Metal X Update 1.0


Ripples:
To turn on ripple effect ON  rename "corner-ripple-ltr1.svg" to "corner-ripple-rtl.svg", then hit Alt+F2 and enter "rt" to restart theme.



The ripple suggestion was given by "rvc-2011" from gnome-look, if anybody has another suggestion plz do let me knw and will try and add them.

  
